---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro'
---

<DocsLayout title="Pricing" description="Commercial model and pricing tiers.">
  <article class="doc-content">
    <h1>Pricing & Commercial Model</h1>

    <blockquote>
      Clearhold is a B2B infrastructure product.<br />
      We don't sell to freelancers. We partner with platforms.
    </blockquote>

    <h2>Pricing Philosophy</h2>

    <p>
      Our pricing reflects what we actually provide: <strong>risk orchestration</strong>, not just
      API calls.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Volume grows → unit cost decreases</li>
      <li>Disputes are premium actions → priced accordingly</li>
      <li>No "unlimited" plans — we scale with you</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Plans</h2>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <h3>Standard</h3>
        <p class="subtitle">Pay-as-you-go</p>
        <div class="price">
          <span class="amount">4.5%</span>
          <span class="plus">+</span>
          <span class="amount">$0.45</span>
          <span class="period">/per execution</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li><strong>Full</strong> lifecycle orchestration</li>
          <li><strong>Dispute-aware</strong> decision engine</li>
          <li><strong>HMAC</strong> security & replay protection</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="includes">
          <p><strong>Includes:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>API-first integration</li>
            <li>Unlimited webhooks</li>
            <li>Comprehensive audit logs</li>
            <li>Developer support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="target">For: Vertical SaaS, Marketplace Platforms</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Enterprise</h3>
        <p class="subtitle">Embedded Core</p>
        <div class="price">
          <span class="amount">Volume-based</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Negotiated pricing</li>
          <li>Custom contractual terms</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="includes">
          <p><strong>Everything in Standard, plus:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Priority Support & SLA</li>
            <li>Dedicated Technical Manager</li>
            <li>On-prem / VPC deployment</li>
            <li>Advanced compliance auditing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="target">For: High-volume enterprise integrators</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>What's Included in All Plans</h2>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Feature</th>
          <th>Included</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Full API access</td>
          <td>✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>HMAC authentication</td>
          <td>✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Webhook delivery</td>
          <td>✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Decision engine</td>
          <td>✓</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Audit trail</td>
          <td>✓</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>What We Don't Charge For</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>✓ API calls (No per-request fees)</li>
      <li>✓ Webhook deliveries & retries</li>
      <li>✓ Metadata storage</li>
      <li>✓ Decision engine queries</li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-accent">✓ Outcome-based fees</strong> (We charge for the decision, not the
        result)
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contract Terms</h2>

    <p>All agreements include:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Decision output = <strong>recommendation</strong> (not enforcement)</li>
      <li>Final enforcement = <strong>client responsibility</strong></li>
      <li>Max liability = fees paid (capped)</li>
      <li>No custody of funds</li>
      <li>No custody of user data</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <p><strong>Ready to integrate?</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:sales@clearhold.io">Contact Sales →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .doc-content {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.1);
  }

  .pricing-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .pricing-card .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .pricing-card .price {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .pricing-card .amount {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .pricing-card .plus {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0.1rem;
  }

  .pricing-card .period {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-left: 0.25rem;
  }

  .pricing-card .features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-card .features li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .pricing-card .includes {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .pricing-card .includes p {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing-card .includes ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pricing-card .includes li {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .pricing-card .target {
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: var(--color-accent-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }
</style>
